data.description: We are offering a downpayment assistance program: $5,000 in closing cost, $500 for appraisal, and $500 for Home Warranty through Motto Mortgage Expert Solutions.  Situated in Walnut Hill, this 4 Unit building is an excellent opportunity to own a turnkey, fully renovated building consisting of 4 residential units offering 2 bedrooms & 1 full bathroom. Occupy one unit and allow the other 3 units to pay for your mortgage or excellent property to add to your rental portfolio. Newly reconstructed in 2021 & offering an upscale design & featuring low maintenance & reduced energy savings costs. The building was constructed with a modern and contemporary design with hardwood flooring & recessed lighting all throughout. Beautifully, designed kitchen features granite countertops, white cabinetry & all new stainless-steel appliances to include Dishwasher, Range, Microwave Oven & Refrigerator. Each unit is self-contained and is equipped with its own heater, hot water heater, heating, central air conditioning and added bonus of laundry hook-up in the unit. Each unit features 2 bedrooms & 1 full bathroom and added privacy with each unit on it's own floor. The first-floor unit provides access to the rear enclosed yard. The building was completely rebuilt and includes all brand-new Heating, Central Air Conditioning, Plumbing & Electric plus easy access with Blue Tooth Intercom System & electric door codes. The 10 Year Tax Abatement has been applied for with the city of Philadelphia.  Buyer needs to do their own due diligence to verify the zoning. Walk Score of 79, Transit Score & Bike Score of 67. Very conveniently located to Walnut St, Chestnut St & Baltimore Ave, Barkan Park, 48th St Cafe, and Reanimator Coffee. In close proximity to University of Pennsylvania, CHOP, University City & public transportation.
